version_description:
- Added “Remember me” to login screen
- Words added to main navigation icons
- Suburb name or multiple locations appears in the search result list view
- New businesses added to the Entertainment program have a flag on top right corner of offer
- New photo carousel for merchant offer pages - click to open the carousel for larger images, doesn’t automatically download all images unless you click into the carousel which reduces data usage
- ‘Gold Award’ and ‘Hall of Fame’ icon appears on businesses
- Review reminders on home page
- Dates added to business reviews
- Value Received improvements with separate dining and eating, activities and retail. Added cents capability.
- Added Entertainment Facebook, Instagram and Twitter to Contact Us page
- General bug fixes
